課程大綱










遙測與地理資訊系統應用THE APPLICATION OF REMOTE SENSING AND GEOGRAPHIC INFORMATION SYSTEM






開課系所 Department/Institute:  水利系          Hydraulic and Ocean Engineering
開課教師 Instructor:   張　懿 Chang, Yi                     
開課學年 Academic Year:   0102
